#Title
Back button closes application

#Description
Back button returns from map page to main page and closes application then

#Pre-conditions
The application is installed

#Steps
1. Run the application
2. Wait until cities list is loaded
3. Scroll down to the 'Aalburg, NL' city
4. Click on 'Aalburg, NL'
5. Wait until map page is loaded
6. Click back button
7. Wait until cities list is loaded
8. Click back button

#Expected result
First back button click returns user from map page to main page
Second back button click closes the application